                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-36-18521122 t18521122-36-punishment-30"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Coleridge and the Fourth Jury.</hi>
               </p>
